SUMMARY:*MUSIC BINGO* (An Afternoon of Fun\, Treats and Great Music!) (Sun
 day April 12th)
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 I'd like to invite you out to a fun-filled afternoon with this fantastic p
 arty social game called **MUSIC BINGO**\n\nEveryone can play (It's easy to
